<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 18:09:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登为内塔尼亚胡铺红地毯是不可原谅的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-03/ty-article/.highlight/for-biden-to-roll-out-the-red-carpet-for-netanyahu-is-inexcusable/00000190-792d-d37b-a59c-fdbfb7040000</link><description>拜登面临着证明他的认知能力和正确判断力的压力。他可以通过在 7 月 24 日国会联席会议上发表讲话时不与内塔尼亚胡会面来证明这两点</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:56:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-03/ty-article/.highlight/for-biden-to-roll-out-the-red-carpet-for-netanyahu-is-inexcusable/00000190-792d-d37b-a59c-fdbfb7040000</guid></item><item><title>地球气候不再可预测了吗？答案将在今年夏天揭晓</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/climate-change/2024-07-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/is-the-earths-climate-no-longer-predictable-the-answer-will-arrive-this-summer/00000190-7306-dbfd-a5d1-f3978a1e0000</link><description>“未知领域”：一项著名的科学实验表明，当系统超过某个阈值时，其行为如何变得混乱且不可预测。气候科学家现在正在争论地球是否已经到了那个关键时刻</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:56:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/climate-change/2024-07-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/is-the-earths-climate-no-longer-predictable-the-answer-will-arrive-this-summer/00000190-7306-dbfd-a5d1-f3978a1e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 271 天：白宫称拜登“可能”在华盛顿会见内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-271-biden-likely-to-meet-netanyahu-in-washington-white-house-says/00000190-796d-d0b6-a9b1-7dfd55970001</link><description>以色列在黎巴嫩南部城市提尔刺杀了真主党高级指挥官 ■ 真主党向以色列北部发射了 100 枚火箭弹作为回应 ■ 以色列国防军主席呼吁“严厉惩罚”袭击安全部队撤离约旦河西岸非法哨所的定居者 ■ 以色列士兵在以色列刺伤袭击中丧生以色列北部 ■ 战争进入 271 天后您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-271-biden-likely-to-meet-netanyahu-in-washington-white-house-says/00000190-796d-d0b6-a9b1-7dfd55970001</guid></item><item><title>真主党高级指挥官在黎巴嫩南部的以色列空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/senior-hezbollah-commander-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-in-southern-lebanon/00000190-7911-dbb2-a3f0-fd5324870000</link><description>穆罕默德·尼玛·纳赛尔指挥真主党阿齐兹部队，在黎巴嫩山谷地区和叙利亚边境沿线开展活动。袭击发生后，大约 100 枚火箭从黎巴嫩发射到以色列北部</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:49:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/senior-hezbollah-commander-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-in-southern-lebanon/00000190-7911-dbb2-a3f0-fd5324870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯人要求劳工法庭撤销因煽动恐怖主义而被解雇的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-asks-labor-court-to-reverse-dismissal-for-incitement-to-terrorism/00000190-78b3-d084-a7dc-f8b7f0ba0000</link><description>来自东耶路撒冷的蒙塔塞尔·阿巴西 (Muntaser Abbasi) 是四个孩子的父亲，10 月 7 日后不久，他因同事对他在个人 WhatsApp 上发布的《古兰经》经文提出投诉而被解雇。阿巴西现在正在努力寻找工作，他对法院维持解雇的决定提出上诉</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:03:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-asks-labor-court-to-reverse-dismissal-for-incitement-to-terrorism/00000190-78b3-d084-a7dc-f8b7f0ba0000</guid></item><item><title>罗杰·沃特斯：以色列编造了哈马斯在 10 月 7 日强奸妇女和谋杀婴儿的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/roger-waters-israel-made-up-hamas-raped-and-murdered-babies-on-october-7/00000190-78dc-d084-a7dc-f8df02280000</link><description>在这位音乐家接受皮尔斯·摩根采访后，以色列妇女组织要求以色列广播电台不要播放沃特斯的歌曲。 Eco99fm回应说：“我们对这次采访感到震惊，在可预见的未来我们不会播放他的歌曲”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:25:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/roger-waters-israel-made-up-hamas-raped-and-murdered-babies-on-october-7/00000190-78dc-d084-a7dc-f8df02280000</guid></item><item><title>埃及新内阁宣誓就职，日益严峻的经济挑战引发公众不满</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/egypt-swears-in-a-new-cabinet-as-mounting-economic-challenges-fuel-public-discontent/00000190-789f-d7ff-a7b2-fbbf501b0000</link><description>由总理穆斯塔法·马德布利担任主席的新内阁包括重大变化，特别是在国防和经济相关的投资组合方面</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/egypt-swears-in-a-new-cabinet-as-mounting-economic-challenges-fuel-public-discontent/00000190-789f-d7ff-a7b2-fbbf501b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部购物中心发生刺伤袭击，以色列国防军士兵身亡，另一人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-another-seriously-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-in-northern-israeli-shopping-mall/00000190-7852-d7ff-a7b2-fbf243dd0000</link><description>警方报告称，行凶者是阿拉伯城镇纳哈夫的一名以色列居民；家人在流传的视频中认出了他的身份后赶到。三人都被戴上手铐，他的兄弟也被绑在腿上，眼睛也被蒙住</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:12:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-another-seriously-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-in-northern-israeli-shopping-mall/00000190-7852-d7ff-a7b2-fbf243dd0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管发生了战争，以色列初创公司在第二季度筹集了更多资金。所有其他消息都是坏消息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-israeli-startups-raised-more-money-all-the-other-news-is-bad/00000190-7868-de25-a3df-7cfbd8900000</link><description>以色列初创公司第二季度筹集了更多资金，但该行业仍处于低迷状态，无处可求助</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:51:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-israeli-startups-raised-more-money-all-the-other-news-is-bad/00000190-7868-de25-a3df-7cfbd8900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸定居点预建 6,000 多套住房</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-advances-over-6-000-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/00000190-7828-d8da-aff3-7f6bc9430000</link><description>上周，财政部长斯莫特里奇宣布政府批准旨在“反对承认巴勒斯坦国”的措施，其中包括授权建造数千套住房并将西岸五个未经授权的前哨基地合法化</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:48:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-advances-over-6-000-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/00000190-7828-d8da-aff3-7f6bc9430000</guid></item><item><title>WZO 批准在赫茨尔墓地举行纪念米里亚姆·阿德尔森的活动，并关闭了公共广场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/wzo-allows-event-honoring-miriam-adelson-at-herzl-burial-site-shutting-down-public-plaza/00000190-77a3-d705-a7f5-fffba9fc0000</link><description>世界犹太复国主义组织主席在没有与该组织领导层讨论该问题的情况下批准了该活动。 WZO 副主席表示，我们不会授权这样做，将其交给慈善家是一个严重的错误。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:55:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/wzo-allows-event-honoring-miriam-adelson-at-herzl-burial-site-shutting-down-public-plaza/00000190-77a3-d705-a7f5-fffba9fc0000</guid></item><item><title>罕见的老式以色列演出海报系列唤起了数十年的音乐记忆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rare-vintage-israeli-gigs-posters-collection-conjures-decades-of-music-memories/00000190-7325-d0bf-a9fd-77fff80c0000</link><description>两名以色列音乐和纪念品爱好者在档案、工具棚、公寓和集装箱中筛选，寻找以色列音乐演出海报。结果在一本新书中呈现</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:01:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rare-vintage-israeli-gigs-posters-collection-conjures-decades-of-music-memories/00000190-7325-d0bf-a9fd-77fff80c0000</guid></item><item><title>新的哥伦比亚大学管理人员文本显示，院长们讨论犹太学生的“特权”和“$$$$”，并抨击希勒尔领导人是“问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/new-columbia-administrator-texts-show-deans-talking-jewish-student-privilege-and/00000190-77d3-d2ab-a7d2-77ffef080000</link><description>虽然短信的内容之前已经报道过，但完整的交流显示，大学官员淡化了学生对反犹太主义的担忧，猛烈抨击了学校校长希勒尔，并暗示犹太学生因为金钱而受到关注</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/new-columbia-administrator-texts-show-deans-talking-jewish-student-privilege-and/00000190-77d3-d2ab-a7d2-77ffef080000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗总统候选人在周五决选前讨论核协议和经济制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/irans-presidential-hopefuls-talk-nuclear-deal-economic-sanctions-ahead-of-friday-runoff/00000190-7772-d705-a7f5-fffb67450000</link><description>伊朗改革派候选人表示，他将努力恢复与世界大国的核协议，而他的强硬派竞争对手则谴责他没有任何计划取消西方国家实施的经济制裁</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:41:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/irans-presidential-hopefuls-talk-nuclear-deal-economic-sanctions-ahead-of-friday-runoff/00000190-7772-d705-a7f5-fffb67450000</guid></item><item><title>定居者在约旦河西岸前哨撤离时与以色列军队发生冲突，投掷燃烧弹和石块</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/settlers-clash-with-israeli-forces-at-west-bank-outpost-throw-firebombs-stones/00000190-773a-de25-a3df-7fbbabd70000</link><description>前哨站的定居者点燃轮胎，向以色列军队投掷石块，以撤离巴勒斯坦私人土地上的建筑，该建筑已经存在了两年但没有得到执行。一名国防官员证实恐怖袭击源自前哨基地，并获得政府批准撤离</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 06:53:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/settlers-clash-with-israeli-forces-at-west-bank-outpost-throw-firebombs-stones/00000190-773a-de25-a3df-7fbbabd70000</guid></item><item><title>在每天接二连三的丑闻之下，内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们转移了人们对以色列不断升级的危机的注意力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-disaster-a-day-government-diverts-attention-away-from-israels-dire-situation/00000190-751c-d705-a7f5-fdff39230000</link><description>希法医院院长获释、加沙电力以及《纽约时报》的一篇报道对以色列人来说没有什么新鲜事：部长们制造并夸大丑闻，希望公众忘记他们持续的失败。政客和他们派往战场的士兵之间的鸿沟从未如此之大</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 03:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-disaster-a-day-government-diverts-attention-away-from-israels-dire-situation/00000190-751c-d705-a7f5-fdff39230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，黎巴嫩空袭后向以色列北部发射了 100 枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-targeted-terror-cell-in-west-bank-drone-strike-palestinians-four-killed/00000190-764d-d6e9-afb6-777d76dc0000</link><description>以色列军队证实暗杀了黎巴嫩真主党高级指挥官 ■ 以色列警方证实，在以色列北部发生的刺杀事件中被枪杀的袭击者是以色列的阿拉伯公民；以色列国防军确认死者为以色列士兵 ■ 国防部长加兰特表示以色列更愿意与黎巴嫩达成协议，但如有必要将与真主党作战 ■ 白宫官员：拜登“可能”本月在华盛顿会见内塔尼亚胡</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-targeted-terror-cell-in-west-bank-drone-strike-palestinians-four-killed/00000190-764d-d6e9-afb6-777d76dc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区数小时内有两人被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-people-shot-and-killed-within-hours-in-israels-arab-community/00000190-7501-d0bf-a9fd-75fbff820000</link><description>周二晚上，一名 15 岁少年也被枪杀 ■ 《国土报》的统计显示，自 2023 年初以来，以色列阿拉伯社区已发生 111 起凶杀案</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-people-shot-and-killed-within-hours-in-israels-arab-community/00000190-7501-d0bf-a9fd-75fbff820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卫生部扣留了在抗议中被拘留的医生的“良好信誉证明”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/health-ministry-withholds-certificate-from-doctor-who-was-detained-at-protest/00000190-74c7-d705-a7f5-fcfff8e50000</link><description>Daphna Shochat 博士在 6 月的一次反政府集会上被拘留，后被无罪释放。即将移居英国的肖查特向卫生部申请了证明，以便她能找到工作。她被拒绝并被告知她有犯罪记录，但警方否认了这一点</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:40:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/health-ministry-withholds-certificate-from-doctor-who-was-detained-at-protest/00000190-74c7-d705-a7f5-fcfff8e50000</guid></item><item><title>一场毁灭性的言论席卷了以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/an-annihilation-discourse-has-taken-over-israel/00000190-735c-d0bf-a9fd-77fe9eda0000</link><description>历史学家本尼·莫里斯和许多其他人（包括左翼人士）呼吁以色列对伊朗发动核攻击，这是毁灭一切的复仇战略的延续。我们必须趁我们还可以的时候走上街头抗议</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:05:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/an-annihilation-discourse-has-taken-over-israel/00000190-735c-d0bf-a9fd-77fe9eda0000</guid></item></channel></rss>